data.description: Stunning in Silvercrest!  This 5 bedroom/4 full bath house is a dream.  The in-ground pool is sure to bring many happy memories for the entire family.  The home is located at the end of a cul-de-sac and is near shopping, restaurants, day-spa, fitness gym, local school tennis courts, a medical center and more! As you enter the home and move past the formal dining room and study your eyes are drawn to the 20 ft ceilings and eye catching fireplace.  To your left you will notice a large kitchen and breakfast nook.  The master suite is sure to dazzle with his/hers closets, separate vanities, and a walk-in shower.  After you make your way up the elegant staircase you will notice the large bedrooms upstairs with a 5th bedroom that has a bath entirely to itself.  With extra parking beside the 2 car garage, granite throughout, a sprinkler system, and the home being wired for security, what more could this home offer?
